863
00:32:29,190 --> 00:32:30,870
that we should just be buddies.

864
00:32:32,500 --> 00:32:34,260
Although we're back together,

865
00:32:35,110 --> 00:32:36,430
I keep feeling like

866
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:39,420
we can never go back
to how things were before.

867
00:32:43,190 --> 00:32:45,740
If that feeling from before is gone,

868
00:32:47,150 --> 00:32:48,700
what's left between us?

869
00:32:52,150 --> 00:32:54,350
How can we maintain our relationship?

870
00:33:11,910 --> 00:33:12,700
Is it time?

871
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:17,740
90 days, 8 hours, and 43 minutes.

872
00:33:17,780 --> 00:33:18,590
It's time.

873
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:19,190
Okay.

874
00:33:21,190 --> 00:33:24,500
- Buddy.
- Buddy.

875
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:28,390
Go!

876
00:33:36,670 --> 00:33:37,500
Go in.

877
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:42,980
It's been three months.
Time to change them.

878
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:44,670
Our three-month internship is over.

879
00:33:44,670 --> 00:33:46,190
Give us black lanyards.

880
00:33:46,290 --> 00:33:47,790
- Black lanyards!
- Black lanyards!

881
00:33:47,950 --> 00:33:48,500
Okay!

882
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:50,150
Congratulations.

883
00:33:51,150 --> 00:33:51,980
Next,

884
00:33:52,060 --> 00:33:54,060
